data.description: This detached three-bedroom 1400 sq foot "straight through" home was built in about 1935 on a most desirable street in Blue Bell Hill, Mt Airy, With good bones, it waits for your sweat equity! The property features a green-walled front yard, a covered front porch, a living room, a dining room, a full bath off the dining room, then a kitchen in the rear. Two bedrooms and one full bath are on the second floor. An additional garret-style bedroom is on the third floor. There is a rear deck and a very deep rear yard. Colonial staircases, decent ceiling height, and a very manageable-sized home!
